<div class="recipes-preview">
  <div class="recipes-preview__header">
    <h2 class="recipes-preview__title">
      <a href="{{ '/recipes/' | relative_url }}">Recipes</a>
    </h2>
    <p>
      I really enjoy cooking, very much the same as doing research. It's not only because my favourate recipes represents my philosophy in doing
      research:
    </p>

    <div class="pull-quote">
      <q>“高端的食材，往往只需要最朴素的烹饪方式。”</q><br>
      <q>"The finest ingredients often require only the simplest cooking methods."</q>
      <span class="cite">— A Bite of China <span class="work">Season 1 (2012), narration</span></span>
    </div>

    <p>but also they comfort a child from Hunan, China when he misses his hometown.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="recipes-preview__grid">
    {% for recipe in site.data.recipes limit: 3 %}
      <article class="recipe-card recipe-card--compact">
        <div class="recipe-card__media{% unless recipe.image %} recipe-card__media--placeholder{% endunless %}">
          {% if recipe.image %}
            <img
              src="{{ '/assets/img/recipes/' | append: recipe.image | relative_url }}"
              alt="{{ recipe.name }}"
              loading="lazy"
            >
          {% else %}
            <span class="recipe-card__placeholder-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-utensils"></i></span>
          {% endif %}
        </div>

        <div class="recipe-card__content">
          {% if recipe.cuisine %}
            <div class="recipe-card__meta">
              <span class="recipe-card__chip">{{ recipe.cuisine }}</span>
            </div>
          {% endif %}

          <h3 class="recipe-card__title">{{ recipe.name }}</h3>
          {% if recipe.name_en %}
            <p class="recipe-card__subtitle">{{ recipe.name_en }}</p>
          {% endif %}

          <p class="recipe-card__description recipe-card__description--compact">
            {{ recipe.description | strip_html | strip | truncate: 135 }}
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  {% if site.data.recipes.size > 3 %}
    <div class="recipes-preview__cta">
      <a href="{{ '/recipes/' | relative_url }}" class="btn btn-outline-primary">View all recipes</a>
    </div>
  {% endif %}
</div>
